/colorContentSelectedHover":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider\/colorcontentselectedhover","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorContentSelectedHover","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token colors.actionHover","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/colorContentSelectedHover","title":"colorContentSelectedHover"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSFilterChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSSuggestionChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"ChipComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") ,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and border  (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}]}}}